{"tid":2358313,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"高盛將所有恒指牛熊證停牌，並撤回上市除牌。","createTime":"2021-01-08T04:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T05:28:47.000Z","uid":7076,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3326f53835667cc1b777844859ffbaef711bbaba","tid":2358313,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"Trump臨別秋波，將多隻中資股列入黑名單。以為只有中芯、中車等股份受影響，實際上美資行已全線避險。高盛將所有恒指牛熊證停牌，並撤回上市除牌。<br />\n<br />\n恒指成份股裡包括中移動、中海油等股份。如果玩得再盡，外資基金避險下，要焗沽恒指相關股份甚至被動指數基金，影響更為深遠。<br />\n<br />\n講多次，今時今日，避險大過天，重倉單一市場及指數，同你一注獨贏一隻股票沒分別。<br />\n<br />\n相關連結：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2021/0107/2021010701263_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2021%2F0107%2F2021010701263_c.pdf&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=e9fb2e83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2021/0107/2021010701263_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0r6zy9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0r6zy9.jpg&h=c4fb530d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d215e572ff6b9f058992b179e3f8ec55549473b1","tid":2358313,"uid":21872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"爆升wo 中芯"},{"pid":"d5e45dc238c4f91797c2c3cebf3ba474efc615bb","tid":2358313,"uid":112985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d215e572ff6b9f058992b179e3f8ec55549473b1","tid":2358313,"uid":21872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"爆升wo 中芯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:00:06.000Z","msg":"國家隊&hellip;this is hong kong market bro"},{"pid":"a850b02fd55ebe8e22b54cd1871d11ac546b0e2a","tid":2358313,"uid":64072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:14:30.000Z","msg":"恆指仲係日日升"},{"pid":"755de44e900022391fc264c8fc2df1ed63eed113","tid":2358313,